    "talent": [
      {
        "key": "轰闪落雷",
        "title": "轰闪落雷",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/16/157749474/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_3061446818060927165.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>普通攻击</color>\n造成1点 <color=#ffacff>雷元素伤害</color> 。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "雾虚之召",
        "title": "雾虚之召",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/16/157749474/ba8a520b631a5349ea54ca1fad2ec264_8644419440078736612.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>元素战技</color>\n召唤 <color=#ffffff>雷萤</color> 。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "霆雷之护",
        "title": "霆雷之护",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/16/157749474/58e7aa03ca09a144cdac07649148383f_1836787288124762040.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>元素爆发</color>\n造成1点 <color=#ffacff>雷元素伤害</color> ，本角色 <color=#ffacff>附着雷元素</color> ，生成 <color=#ffffff>雷萤护罩</color> 并准备技能 <color=#ffffff>霆电迸发</color> 。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "雷元素伤害",
        "title": "雷元素伤害",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/16/157749474/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_704508979076666259.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "附着雷元素，可发生元素反应：\n【 <color=#ffacff>雷元素</color> + <color=#ff9999>火元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>超载</color> ：本伤害 +2，目标强制切换到下一个角色\n【 <color=#ffacff>雷元素</color> + <color=#99ffff>冰元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>超导</color> ：本伤害 +1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害\n【 <color=#ffacff>雷元素</color> + <color=#80c0ff>水元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>感电</color> ：本伤害 +1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害\n【 <color=#ffacff>雷元素</color> + <color=#99ff88>草元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>原激化</color> ：本伤害 +1，生成使下3次草/雷伤害+1的[ <color=#ffffff>激化领域</color> ]"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "雷萤",
        "title": "雷萤",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/16/157749474/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_226177063543352414.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>召唤物</color>\n<color=#ffffff>结束阶段：</color> 造成1点 <color=#ffacff>雷元素伤害</color> 。\n<color=#ffffff>可用次数：3</color>\n<color=#ffffff>敌方累计打出3张行动牌后：</color> 此牌 <color=#ffffff>可用次数</color> +1。（最多叠加到3）\n<color=#ffffff>愚人众·雷萤术士受到元素反应伤害后：</color> 此牌 <color=#ffffff>可用次数</color> -1。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": [],
        "talentImg": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/16/157749474/c32e8d1f898b13385973738aba9d5c6a_2077134023659171113.png"
      },
      {
        "key": "规则术语",
        "title": "规则术语",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/16/157749474/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_6692676922015699056.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffffff>可用次数</color>\n此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次 <color=#ffffff>可用次数</color> ；\n<color=#ffffff>可用次数</color> 耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。\n<color=#ffffff>护盾</color>\n此护盾所保护的角色受到伤害时，将会消耗护盾来抵消伤害。\n<color=#ffacff>附着雷元素</color>\n不通过伤害附着雷元素时，发生的元素反应会忽略伤害效果：\n<color=#ffffff>超载：</color> 目标强制切换到下一个角色\n<color=#ffffff>超导：</color> 没有效果\n<color=#ffffff>感电：</color> 没有效果\n<color=#ffffff>原激化：</color> 生成使下2次草元素或雷元素伤害+1的[ <color=#ffffff>激化领域</color> ]\n<color=#ffffff>雷萤护罩</color>\n<color=#ffd780>护盾</color>\n为我方出战角色提供 <color=#ffffff>1点护盾</color> 。\n<color=#ffffff>创建时：</color> 如果我方场上存在 <color=#ffffff>雷萤</color> ，则额外提供其 <color=#ffffff>可用次数</color> 的 <color=#ffffff>护盾</color> 。（最多额外提供3点 <color=#ffffff>护盾</color> ）\n<color=#ffffff>霆电迸发</color>\n<color=#ffd780>元素爆发</color>\n（需准备1个行动轮）\n造成2点 <color=#ffacff>雷元素伤害</color> 。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      }
    ],
